<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/37218899-kelly">Kelly</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I don&apos;t believe so, the great thing about this book to me is that there is a deeper thought throughout the book and a great ending. It challenges us t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I don't believe so, the great thing about this book to me is that there is a deeper thought throughout the book and a great ending. It challenges us to see beyond our circumstances to a newer perspective on things where ever we are at in our lives! A MUST READ! <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
