        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2268183402" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3357549606963825174">The Noticer over all I thought was a good book, it’s talks of a man named Jones that comes into people’s life when they need it most, he tells them that finding a new perspective on what is happening in you’re life can change the way you see it from bad to good. I think that’s what we all need to do, find the good perspectives not the bad ones. </span>

          </span>
